data.description: Beautiful, extremely well maintained craftsman home on a large lot with an excellent Jefferson location! Tons of custom features and meticulously crafted interior seamlessly blend comfort and style. Upgraded chandeliers and light fixtures throughout. Coffered ceilings in the formal dining room add just the right amount of elegance while the breakfast nook immediately off of the kitchen allows for everyday living. Granite countertops, upgraded oven and refrigerator along with huge breakfast bar make the kitchen a real treat! Vaulted ceilings in the two story living room perfectly complement the fireplace providing the perfect space to relax, entertain or enjoy with family and friends!  Owner's suite features tray ceilings complete with an en suite, spa like bathroom with soaking tub, separate tiled shower, double vanity and walk-in closet. Flex space over the garage can be used as a bedroom, office, nursery, however you see fit! Enjoy entertaining on the covered front porch or in the privacy of the fenced backyard. Subdivision amenities to include pool, walking trails, clubhouse, and playground. Convenient to I-85, downtown Jefferson as well as a short commute to Athens, Commerce and Braselton. Fantastic find, especially in a low inventory market. Transferrable 2-10 home warranty included! Schedule your showing today!
